Silly.

62
00:06:20,519 --> 00:06:21,920
I have an Innate Sacred Body.

63
00:06:22,360 --> 00:06:23,480
Impervious to evil.

64
00:06:26,199 --> 00:06:27,800
But I just dreamt of my mom.

65
00:06:29,639 --> 00:06:30,680
I know.

66
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:34,160
Since the legend of The Serpent's Wedding is fake...

67
00:06:36,199 --> 00:06:37,639
...then what happened to my mom back then...

68
00:06:38,839 --> 00:06:40,120
...must have a hidden story.

69
00:07:13,879 --> 00:07:15,120
I remember everything now.

70
00:07:17,040 --> 00:07:19,160
I saw my mom's body with my own eyes.

71
00:07:20,439 --> 00:07:22,639
There was no Serpent's Wedding at all.

72
00:07:23,319 --> 00:07:24,480
Growing up...

73
00:07:25,279 --> 00:07:26,839
...that's what you always told me.

74
00:07:29,079 --> 00:07:30,000
Why?

75
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:33,160
Why did you lie to me?

76
00:07:50,639 --> 00:07:51,480
Say something!

77
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:55,519
What exactly are you hiding from me?

78
00:08:02,720 --> 00:08:03,959
Sometimes...

79
00:08:04,839 --> 00:08:06,800
...living a bit obliviously...

80
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:09,560
...makes life easier.

81
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:11,920
What's past...

82
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:14,000
...let it stay in the past.

83
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,800
How can I possibly let it go?

84
00:08:22,639 --> 00:08:23,480
For so many years...

85
00:08:23,839 --> 00:08:25,439
...whenever I close my eyes, I see...

86
00:08:25,439 --> 00:08:27,319
...a Procession of the Long Immortal taking my mom away.

87
00:08:28,279 --> 00:08:29,560
I want to save her...

88
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:32,360
...but I can't.

89
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:34,360
Uncle

90
00:08:35,559 --> 00:08:36,480
Tell me.

91
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:39,480
How can I let it go?

92
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:54,039
I beg you.

93
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:57,320
I just want an answer.

94
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:59,720
How did my mom die?

95
00:09:04,799 --> 00:09:05,879
Master

96
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:09,679
What exactly is going on?

97
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,159
Very well.

98
00:09:26,759 --> 00:09:29,840
It's time I let you know the truth.

99
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:36,000
When I first met your mother...

100
00:09:45,039 --> 00:09:45,480
Brother.

101
00:09:45,759 --> 00:09:46,600
This is...

102
00:09:48,039 --> 00:09:49,159
This is my college classmate.

103
00:09:49,399 --> 00:09:50,360
Her name is Yulan.

104
00:09:50,759 --> 00:09:51,480
Hello, Sister Lan.

105
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:53,120
Hello.

106
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:54,919
Sister Lan looks so...

107
00:09:54,919 --> 00:09:56,480
virtuous, beautiful, and generous.

108
00:09:58,080 --> 00:09:58,720
Sister Lan.

109
00:09:58,720 --> 00:09:59,519
Let me tell you,

110
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:00,799
we have so many...

111
00:10:00,799 --> 00:10:01,879
fun places and good food here.

112
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:03,320
When we have time later,

113
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:04,679
I'll take you out to have some fun.

114
00:10:05,320 --> 00:10:06,200
Really?

115
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,440
Sister, have some tea.

116
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:12,759
Thank you.

117
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,600
Do you want some snacks?

118
00:10:26,799 --> 00:10:28,720
We fell in love at first sight.

119
00:10:29,559 --> 00:10:31,200
We regretted not meeting sooner.

120
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:35,159
But I ignored Big Brother's feelings.

121
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:37,639
Brother.

122
00:10:40,159 --> 00:10:40,519
Sister.

123
00:10:40,840 --> 00:10:41,600
Do you know where my brother...

124
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,360
...went?

125
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,320
Your brother...

126
00:10:43,320 --> 00:10:44,559
Your brother just went out.

127
00:10:46,759 --> 00:10:48,320
Sister, there's something on your head.

128
00:11:10,879 --> 00:11:12,360
My brother seems to care about you too.

129
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,080
Impossible.

130
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:14,759
We're just ordinary classmates.

131
00:11:19,639 --> 00:11:20,960
I'll beat you to death!

132
00:11:22,600 --> 00:11:23,200
Brother!

133
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:25,679
Stop hitting him!

134
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:30,039
What is going on?

135
00:11:32,919 --> 00:11:34,200
Stop fighting!

136
00:11:35,879 --> 00:11:36,639
Mom!

137
00:11:38,919 --> 00:11:39,720
Mom!

138
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:42,080
Mom, what's wrong, Mom?

139
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:42,559
Mom!

140
00:11:43,279 --> 00:11:43,720
Mom!

141
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:44,679
Wake up, Mom!
